  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/ef8e44ab3ca786037c3fb51b1df5cbef.avif?t=1739210501\" width=586 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Towers & Goblins: The Last Stand\" is a fun tower defense game where you plan strategies to fight off crafty goblins.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/1741aababd2dc4c3c75e507b47b3775d.avif?t=1739210501\" width=588 height=140 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Resist Goblin Waves</strong>: Fight off various types of goblins to protect your kingdom from destruction. Goblins attack in waves, giving you time to see their approach and prepare your defenses accordingly. Use this interval to strategize and utilize the geographic advantages of your kingdom to enhance your defense.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/5ce5d33c2e40a24228a5744c0ae57ae6.poster.avif?t=1739210501\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/5ce5d33c2e40a24228a5744c0ae57ae6.webm?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/5ce5d33c2e40a24228a5744c0ae57ae6.mp4?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Build and Upgrade</strong>: Construct towers and walls with your resources. Make them stronger to keep goblins out even longer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/82419d54b1b6b84f0242e60d228d66ca.poster.avif?t=1739210501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/82419d54b1b6b84f0242e60d228d66ca.webm?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/82419d54b1b6b84f0242e60d228d66ca.mp4?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Increase and Manage Population:</strong> Recruit units like pawns and warriors to help expand and defend your kingdom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/93eea2eafc668ad9e2de817dc002810e.poster.avif?t=1739210501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/93eea2eafc668ad9e2de817dc002810e.webm?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/93eea2eafc668ad9e2de817dc002810e.mp4?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Gather and Manage Resources</strong>: Collect essential resources like wood, stone, and gold. Manage your population and ensure there is enough food to sustain it.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/9ef29af361ac34164e9ca22778b07e3c.poster.avif?t=1739210501\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/9ef29af361ac34164e9ca22778b07e3c.webm?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/9ef29af361ac34164e9ca22778b07e3c.mp4?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/ef8e44ab3ca786037c3fb51b1df5cbef.avif?t=1739210501\" width=586 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Towers & Goblins: The Last Stand\" is a fun tower defense game where you plan strategies to fight off crafty goblins.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/1741aababd2dc4c3c75e507b47b3775d.avif?t=1739210501\" width=588 height=140 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Resist Goblin Waves</strong>: Fight off various types of goblins to protect your kingdom from destruction. Goblins attack in waves, giving you time to see their approach and prepare your defenses accordingly. Use this interval to strategize and utilize the geographic advantages of your kingdom to enhance your defense.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/5ce5d33c2e40a24228a5744c0ae57ae6.poster.avif?t=1739210501\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/5ce5d33c2e40a24228a5744c0ae57ae6.webm?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875570/extras/5ce5d33c2e40a24228a5744c0ae57ae6.mp4?t=1739210501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Build and Upgrade</strong>: Construct towers and walls with your resources. Make them stronger to keep goblins out even longer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_